licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

The original TradingAgents framework is the foundation of the multi-agent LLM pipeline
(LangGraph orchestration, agent prompts, memory/reflection system, data vendor routing).

This project adapts and extends the original work for the Indian stock market (NSE/BSE)
with additional features including:
- Support/Resistance, Pivot Points, Cyclical Patterns analysis
- Market Scanner (Gap / Volume / Breakout detection across NIFTY 50/100/BSE 250)
- Unified Recommendation Engine combining multiple signals
- FastAPI backend with WebSocket streaming
- Next.js frontend (trading terminal UI)
- Strategy Performance Tracker
- Seasonal Backtest
- Position Size Calculator
- News aggregator (RSS + yfinance) with customizable sources
- API key management via UI (no .env required)
- Multi-provider LLM support with cost tracking

